⸻

🚀 Updates – Configuration and Teams Notifications – July 2025

📍 All the features below are available in the “Settings” page of the Le Comptoir application.
⚙️ They are disabled by default and can be enabled or disabled individually.

⸻

🕒 New Setting – Define High Wait Time Threshold

It is now possible to configure the duration after which wait time is considered high at the desk.
	•	This setting impacts certain Teams notifications, such as:
	•	the check-in alert
	•	team mobilization
	•	Default value: 15 minutes
	•	The threshold can be adjusted directly in the Settings page.

⸻

